The Lookout;;74;;87;;R;;Chris (Joseph Gordon-Levitt), a star athlete, has the world at his feet. Then a devastating car accident leaves him with brain damage and his bright future dimmed. He takes a job as a bank janitor and must write everything down in a small notepad in order to remember. Some former schoolmates lure Chris into their inner circle and rope him into helping them carry out a heist at the bank.;;Drama,Crime,Mystery & thriller;;Scott Frank;;2007;;Joseph Gordon-Levitt,Jeff Daniels,Carla Gugino,Matthew Goode,Isla Fisher,Alex Borstein,Morgan Kelly,Bruce McGill;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lookout